---
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-photo">
    <img src="/photo_la_gaille_1.jpg" alt="La Gaille, humoriste stand-up" />
    <div class="photo-title">
      <span class="photo-title-text">La Gaille</span>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="label">Stand-up · One-man-show</p>
      <p class="subtitle"><em>Entre Rire et Réalité</em></p>
      <p class="teaser">Un ingénieur qui a troqué son clavier pour un micro. L'histoire d'une reconversion, racontée avec autodérision et une lucidité désarmante.</p>
      <a href="#dates" class="btn-primary">Voir les dates &darr;</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding-top: 68px;
  }

  .hero-photo {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    line-height: 0;
  }

  .hero-photo img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  .photo-title {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    right: 6%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .photo-title-text {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 7.5rem);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-style: italic;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    color: #ffffff;
    text-shadow:
      0 2px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.4),
      0 0 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    display: block;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .hero-content {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem 4.5rem;
    border-top: 3px solid var(--color-accent);
  }

  .hero-content .container {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .label {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
  }

  .teaser {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    max-width: 55ch;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--color-cta-bg);
    color: var(--color-cta-text);
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s;
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: #333;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .photo-title-text {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 10vw, 3.5rem);
    }

    .hero-content {
      padding: 2rem 1.5rem 3rem;
    }
  }
</style>
